1 
Q:
Fail to rosmake
A:
The package is not in your package path probably. Try
export ROS_PACKAGE_PATH=$ROS_PACKAGE_PATH:`pwd`
and rosmake again.

2
Q:
 [rospack] Error: package 'demo_lidar' depends on non-existent package 'opencv2' and rosdep claims that it is not a system dependency. Check the ROS_PACKAGE_PATH or try calling 'rosdep update'

A:
简单的说，就是indigo版本以后，opencv的包，就不叫opencv2了，改成cv_bridge即可。

3
Q:[rospack] Error: depends on non-existent package 'cv_bridge' and rosdep claims that it is not a system dependency. Check the ROS_PACKAGE_PATH or try calling 'rosdep update'
A:
$sudo apt-get install ros-kinetic-cv-bridge

4
Q:[rospack] Error: depends on non-existent package 'pcl_ros' and rosdep claims that it is not a system dependency. Check the ROS_PACKAGE_PATH or try calling 'rosdep update'
A:
$sudo apt-get install ros-kinetic-pcl_ros
其他类推

5
Q:
cannot convert (type ‘sensor_msgs::PointCloud2 {aka sensor_msgs::PointCloud
A:
添加#include <pcl_conversions/pcl_conversions.h>

6
Q:/usr/local/include/opencv2/contrib/openfabmap.hpp:330:24: error: template argument 2 is invalid        map<int, vector<int> > testInvertedMap;                           ^   /usr/local/include/opencv2/contrib/openfabmap.hpp:330:24: error: template argument
A:
注释相关h文件

7
Q: 
/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libboost_system.so: error adding symbols: 
A:
添加　target_link_libraries(ABC boost_system boost_filesystem)
例如
rosbuild_add_executable(featureTracking src/featureTracking.cpp)
TARGET_LINK_LIBRARIES(featureTracking boost_system boost_filesystem)

8 isam 环境搭建
sudo apt-get install cmake libsuitesparse-dev libeigen3-dev libsdl1.2-dev doxygen graphviz

